# Bustan-e-Rahmat Design System

Full reference: `apps/web/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md`  
Tokens: `apps/web/src/styles/tokens.css`

## Colors & tokens

- Never hardcode hex in components; use `var(--color-*)`, `var(--bg-*)`, `var(--text-*)`, `var(--brand-*)`.
- Page background is `var(--bg-base)` (warm cream `#f6eddd`), not pure white.
- Brand palette is **teal + gold only** — no purple, blue, or red accents.
- Cards: `background: var(--bg-surface)`, `border: 1px solid var(--border-default)`, `border-radius: var(--radius-xl)`.

## Typography

- English headings: `var(--font-en-display)` (Cormorant Garamond).
- English body: `var(--font-en-body)` (DM Sans).
- Accent labels / badges: `var(--font-en-accent)` (Cinzel), uppercase, `letter-spacing: 0.08em`.
- Urdu display: `var(--font-urdu-display)` (Noto Nastaliq Urdu).
- Urdu body: `var(--font-urdu-body)` (Noto Naskh Arabic).
- Quran ayat: `class="quran"`, `lang="ar"`, `var(--font-arabic)` (Indopak Nastaleeq, self-hosted).

## Layout & components

- Section vertical padding: `var(--space-section)` (5rem).
- Container max width: `var(--container-max)` (1200px), centered.
- Buttons: `border-radius: var(--radius-full)`, teal bg (`var(--brand-primary)`), cream text (`var(--text-inverse)`); hover adds `var(--shadow-gold)`.
- Styling approach: **CSS Modules** per component — co-locate `Component.tsx` + `Component.module.css`.
- Islamic decorative elements use teal or gold only.

## Do not

- Use Inter/Roboto/system fonts for headings.
- Use English fonts on Urdu text.
- Use pure white `#ffffff` as page background.
- Add colors outside the teal/gold/cream/ink palette.

## Content & data

- All copy lives under `apps/web/src/content/` as typed bilingual `{ ur, en }` objects — never inline string literals in components.
- Landing copy: `apps/web/src/content/site.ts`
- Courses: `apps/web/src/content/courses/` using `Course`, `CourseVersion`, `Module`, `Lesson` from `index.ts`
- Never hand-inline module/lesson lists in page components
